---
title: Seared Sesame Tuna over Rice with Ginger Aioli and Arugula Radish Salad
description: Ginger and garlic are an aioli match made in heaven and the perfect dressing for our seared ahi tuna. We round out this  quick and easy meal with the addition of hearty basmati rice, peppery arugula, and crunchy radishes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-sesame-tuna-over-rice-93011719.jpg
